he compliance function at ransomware hacking firms. In general, any sort of=
 firm will have to decide what level of crime it is optimal to commit. For =
a normal=C2=A0company, I think the conventional wisdom is that the optimal =
level of crime is low, but probably slightly higher than=C2=A0zero. Meanwhi=
